Raising a New Flag — Armada Brewing




































































December  1, 2015



John Kraszewski



Raising a New Flag



December  1, 2015



John Kraszewski












Today we raise a new flag for the Armada! Our journey has only just begun and we are proud to announce that we will be docking in my home state of Connecticut. Though a physical location has not been secured yet I am working to open in my hometown of West Haven. In Spring 2016 I will be moving to Connecticut with my family to get things rolling. In the mean time we will continue to raise capital and do events in Chicago. Chicago will always be a second home to Armada and we want to thank everyone who helped support us and get us this far. We will try to make sure we get product out to you as soon as we can. Why the move? Family. I want to share this journey with my family and do something great in my home state. We look forward to our move and you joining us on our journey. 




John Kraszewski

















